{"tid":1296565,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《認真》大型活動人人都要有planning","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T17:32:36.000Z","uid":263218,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2448da851a9f58bdadf1d3e1e360085a242428","tid":1296565,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:54:19.000Z","msg":"社福界搞一個大型 mass program流程如下 <br />\n<br />\n建議大家如果投身社福活動前，每個人都應該要有自己一個plan <br />\n<br />\n1. 踩線選址/ 思考活動理念、目的及手段<br />\n2. 活動宣傳/ 招募<br />\n3. 準備物資/ 估算人手<br />\n4. 腦內預演 （大致流程、brainstorming 新ideas、對方會點做 )<br />\n5. 準備緊急應對方案/ 疏散計劃<br />\n6. 運作當日<br />\n7. 合作分工<br />\n8. 活動完結時間 / 需考慮會否延長<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大型活動要管理，你我齊心做得到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9becc4f35451fffd39509634d65d79515053805c","tid":1296565,"uid":252662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:55:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66cf84902be8eb9ed20da1497af1d6eaeba6ad05","tid":1296565,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:55:35.000Z","msg":"好似睇到有部份活動 冇好準備 <br />\n大家都有少少緊張 <br />\n<br />\n經一事 蔡一智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fcb0d128624b3a1d89f7daf5e01b41d8e0253f","tid":1296565,"uid":263218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9becc4f35451fffd39509634d65d79515053805c","tid":1296565,"uid":252662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:55:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"自己要有撤退plan"},{"pid":"38c7027d5a4b8700db055b90a8d96f448539c7a9","tid":1296565,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"遊擊可以係策略 但前提係要有成果及意義<br />\n<br />\n琴日比人夾時 大家急急腳走 <br />\n<br />\n又唔知走去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b15b71aebca99efe22fb10d83d